      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "TIGGERLONG BINGO (6) boasts a strong record this course with 22 wins and six minors from 33 tries. Scored by 7 lengths last time (17.97) in a NG over 320m at this track. With a clean break looks hard to beat. LATCH ON (8) has a strong record this track and trip with four wins and four placings from 10 starts. Below best last time at Temora (26.25) in a Grade 4/5, finishing a 4 length fourth. Looks a key chance on best figures. PAW REX (2) produced a modest effort most recently when eighth at Temora over 457m behind Secret Joker (26.95) in a Grade 5. Was in the money the start prior. Solid formlines coming through his last run. Can figure in the finish. HOTTIE DAVIES (4) comes off a (22.91) win last time, scoring by 0.8 lengths in a Grade 4/5 over 400m at this track. Already a winner from this draw.",
